{"prompt": "Create a platform for a local historical reenactment group. The design should be engaging, featuring a cheerful yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Local Historical Reenactment Group</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fff3e0; /* A soft, off-white background */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #ffeb3b; /* Cheerful yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #fdd835; /* A slightly darker yellow for navigation */\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #333;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #f57f17; /* A warm orange on hover */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .main-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #f9a825; /* A rich yellow-orange */\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #f9a825;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .event-list {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        .event-list li {\n            background-color: #fff9c4; /* A very light yellow for list items */\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            padding: 10px;\n            border-left: 4px solid #fdd835;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .event-list li:hover {\n            background-color: #fff59d;\n        }\n        .contact-info {\n            background-color: #fff9c4;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #fdd835; /* Consistent yellow theme */\n            color: #333;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            margin: 15px auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>The Chronicle Keepers</h1>\n        <p>Bringing History to Life</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#events\">Upcoming Events</a>\n        <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact Us</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"main-content\">\n            <h2>About Our Group</h2>\n            <p>Welcome to The Chronicle Keepers, your local historical reenactment group dedicated to preserving and showcasing the vibrant history of our region. We are a passionate community of individuals who love to immerse ourselves in the past, from detailed costumes to accurate historical portrayals.</p>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/600x300/ffeb3b/333?text=Reenactment+Scene\" alt=\"Historical Reenactment Scene\">\n            <p>Our aim is to educate and entertain through authentic demonstrations, interactive displays, and engaging storytelling. We cover various historical periods, focusing on the everyday lives, battles, and cultural practices of our ancestors.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"events\" class=\"main-content\">\n            <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>\n            <ul class=\"event-list\">\n                <li><strong>June 15th, 2024:</strong> Medieval Fair at Old Town Square. Experience the sights and sounds of the 14th century!</li>\n                <li><strong>July 20th, 2024:</strong> Revolutionary War Muster at Heritage Park. Witness thrilling tactical demonstrations.</li>\n                <li><strong>August 10th, 2024:</strong> Victorian Day Picnic - Join us for a leisurely afternoon in period attire.</li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"gallery\" class=\"main-content\">\n            <h2>Gallery</h2>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/ffeb3b/333?text=Costume+Detail\" alt=\"Detailed Costume\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/ffeb3b/333?text=Group+Photo\" alt=\"Group of Reenactors\">\n            <p>See more of our adventures and historical craftsmanship in our online gallery!</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-info\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Interested in joining us or booking an event? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@chroniclekeepers.local</p>\n            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n            <p><strong>Follow us on social media:</strong> [Link to Social Media]</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2024 The Chronicle Keepers. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}